dismissalText.commentary: Abhishek Sharma c Jaiswal b Theekshana 24 (11b 5x4 0x6 16m) SR: 218.18

dismissalComment.html: taken at cover point! Jaiswal only had to grab it with both hands after moving a step to his right! Theekshana bowled a short delivery which was wide enough for any batter to slap for a boundary, only for Abhishek to end up slashing it away from his body to break another stunning stand with Head. RR and I can take a breather, at least for now
